<!DOCTYPE html>
<HTML>
<Head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, minimal-ui">
  <Title>Minecraft 伺服器狀態人造衛星</Title>
  <base target="_blank" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      padding-top: 80px;
    }
    .mccolor {
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      color: transparent; /* Hide unformatted text. */
    }
    #disconnected {
      display: none;
    }
  </style>
</Head>
<Body role="document">
  <div class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top" role="navigation">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="navbar-header">
        <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
          <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </button>
        <span class="navbar-brand">
          <i class="fa fa-globe"></i>
          Minecraft 伺服器狀態人造衛星
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          <li><a href="http://minecraft.net/">Minecraft 官方網站</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://www.minecraft-hk.com/">MCHK</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://hkcdc.org/">HKCDC</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container" role="main">
    <div class="alert alert-danger" id="disconnected" role="alert">
      <b>不好! 斷線了!</b><br />
      線路不穩中... 正在嘗試再次連線...
    </div>
    <noscript>
      <div class="alert alert-danger" id="disconnected" role="alert">
        此系統需要使用 JavaScript, 請先啟動 JavaScript 或者轉用支援 JavaScript 的瀏覽器, 謝謝.
      </div>
    </noscript>
    <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">
        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        <span class="sr-only">Close</span>
      </button>
      <b>注意!</b> 如果想增加自己的伺服器, 請前往
      <a href="http://www.minecraft-hk.com/forum-45-1.html">MCHK</a> /
      <a href="http://bbs.hkcdc.org/forum-672-1.html">HKCDC</a>
      論壇各自的伺服器版塊新增, 這裡將在稍候時間自動取得你的伺服器資料.
    </div>
    <div class="panel panel-primary info">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title"><span class="fa fa-info-circle"></span>
          伺服器狀態列表
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body" id="slist">
        {{#status}}
          {{>status}}
        {{/status}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
